hat brought you to the Vazaelle server?<br><br>Whiz bought the EQ game for me for Christmas because I didn't like Icewind Dale at the time. (He noticed I liked Diablo and how I really liked customizing my character with stats -- gave me such individuality and control -- so he was experimenting with which &quot;roleplaying&quot; games would appeal to me.) Since the game was more for me than for us at the time, I was on my own when I installed the game and had to pick the server. (Whiz did not try to play until two weeks later to see why I was on the game so much.) I saw a message that said recommended servers were highlighted in green (about five of them). I picked Vazaelle because the name was unique enough and I figured I'd remember it whenever I logged in. Server population didn't really factor in too much because I thought maybe more people meant more friends and more people to help me figure out how to play the game! <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :p --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/tongue.gif ALT=":p"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br><br>I had no idea what PvP was so I'm glad I didn't pick the Zeks by accident since I've heard horror stories of people unintentionally starting there. I talked to Whizbang months later about servers and he told me that if he had been the one to pick the servers, he would have started us on a roleplaying one. I just found that interesting how such a small thing can decide the kind of people we'd meet and end up with.<br><br>What about you?<br><br><!--EZCODE IMAGE START--><img src="http://www.lby3.com/eq/leopa/sigs/casual.gif"><!--EZCODE IMAGE END--> <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub78.ezboard.com/ufieni.showPublicProfile?language=EN>fieni</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Hero</span><br> <font color=#00F500>(1/14/02 1:26:49 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub78.ezboard.com/fwalkersofvazaellefrm4.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=393.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Why Vazaelle?</span><hr size=1> Nearly the same: vazaelle was listed as green server. I wasn't sure what it means but... we chose it... <br><br>And I am still not sure I understand what pvp means :-) <p>Fieni Fired - Walkers of vazaelle</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub78.ezboard.com/uleopapanthera.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Leopa Panthera</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Knight</span><br> <font color=#00F500>(1/14/02 1:29:09 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub78.ezboard.com/fwalkersofvazaellefrm4.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=393.topic&index=2>Reply</a>    <br>Community Supporter<br> </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Why Vazaelle?</span><hr size=1> Player versus player. Next time a newbie asks you for stuff, you just kill them on the spot. No duels needed. <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub78.ezboard.com/uackkk.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Ackkk</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Veteran</span><br> <font color=#00F500>(1/14/02 2:18:01 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub78.ezboard.com/fwalkersofvazaellefrm4.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=393.topic&index=3>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Why Vazaelle?</span><hr size=1> i THINK* Ely picked it cause it was green, i picked it cause he did and ranted and raved about his friends so much. He explained the servers and that i could choose any one, but to play with him on the game it had to be Vazaelle, so i knew right off where i was gonna be.<br>i remember him explaining that Whiz and Leopa were married in RL and you can get married on the game, and started thinking WOW! REAL people, from across the world, this could be fun! still bucked up against it because i didn't have my new computer yet, hehe, but after he would log at ungodly hours in the morning, i would every now and then get up and log onto his acct, onto Candle, a human wizard i made on his acct at the time or there was a de chick too i think...and get aggravated that i knew NOTHING and everyone was running and running, looked like everyone was in some big hurry and i couldn't find anything to get into a hurry about, except when i died and not sure i knew to run to the guards even when that happened.<br>LOL! doh! ok, TMI! Sorry, i ramble ALOT! heheheheheh<br><br>I LOVE BEING A WALKER!!<br>-AZIL-<br><br>I LOVE BEING A WALKER!!<br>-AZIL- <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub78.ezboard.com/uwhizbangdustyboots.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Whizbang Dustyboots</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Noble</span><br> <font color=#00F500>(1/14/02 2:45:39 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub78.ezboard.com/fwalkersofvazaellefrm4.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=393.topic&index=4>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Why Vazaelle?</span><hr size=1> Candle's a good name for a wizard, Azil! I like that.<br><br>And yeah, if it had been open at the time, I would have wanted to start on FV. Barring that, Vazaelle was the best choice, for many, many reasons ... had I known any of them! <p><a href="http://eq.guildmagic.com/character.cfm?ID=49189" target="_blank"><img src="http://www.lby3.com/eq/whiz/whiz-banner-long-3.gif" height=60 width=468 alt="Whizbang Dustyboots" border=0></a></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub78.ezboard.com/ularnlobos.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Larn Lobos</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Veteran</span><br> <font color=#00F500>(1/14/02 3:27:35 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub78.ezboard.com/fwalkersofvazaellefrm4.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=393.topic&index=5>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Why Vazaelle?</span><hr size=1> Being one of the last five people on the planet who read the manuals BEFORE playing the game...I'd read about green servers, and about server population.<br><br>When I logged in, Vazaelle was a green server. At the time I logged in, it had the fewest people online. So I picked it.<br><br>(A note to any newbies...when you log into the EQ server now, you just see the server's name and UP or DOWN...before, it actually showed you how many people were online on each server at the time.)<br><br><br>Larn<br> <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub78.ezboard.com/ufieni.showPublicProfile?language=EN>fieni</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Hero</span><br> <font color=#00F500>(1/14/02 9:04:53 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub78.ezboard.com/fwalkersofvazaellefrm4.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=393.topic&index=6>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Why Vazaelle?</span><hr size=1> And for the fun, as some knows, my char was created originaly by my son. At this time I was playing also a druid on another server.... But I was NOT able to find again on which server he was!!!!!!!!<br>Never was patient enough to make all server.....<br>LOL! <p>Fieni Fired - Walkers of vazaelle</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub78.ezboard.com/unilsvitale.showPublicProfile?language=EN>nilsvitale</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Adventurer</span><br> <font color=#00F500>(1/14/02 11:53:10 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub78.ezboard.com/fwalkersofvazaellefrm4.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=393.topic&index=7>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Why Vazaelle?</span><hr size=1> Because the server was only a few months old when i started playing...How I found that out, I have no idea<br><br>Ulrich <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub78.ezboard.com/uvamprissx.showPublicProfile?language=EN>VamprissX</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Veteran</span><br> <font color=#00F500>(1/15/02 3:35:59 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub78.ezboard.com/fwalkersofvazaellefrm4.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=393.topic&index=8>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Why Vazaelle?</span><hr size=1> Most people choose Vazaelle.....I guess in my case, Vazaelle chose me. <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br><br>I started playing EQ on Mithaniel Marr (still have a 50 enchanter there) and then moved to Luclin. After trying Antonius Bayle with my Euro guild and hating the lag, I transfered back to Luclin...so I thought. They accidentally placed me on Vazaelle!<br><br>lol - you should have seen me frantically switching between Luclin and AB, scratching my head and saying WTF!?! when there was no characters to choose from. Verant was non-responsive, so I searched EVERY server (&quot;V&quot; being waaaay down at the bottom) <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :p --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/tongue.gif ALT=":p"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br><br>I almost quit EQ when Verant Customer Service said I could not go back to Luclin. While I miss my friends there, I would not change anything now!! I am happy that Vazaelle chose me! <p>Vampriss<BR>Warlock<BR>Walkers<p>< insert scary necro design here ></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub78.ezboard.com/uabinsuranautishzaar.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Abinsuran Autishzaar</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Veteran</span><br> <font color=#00F500>(1/15/02 5:45:41 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub78.ezboard.com/fwalkersofvazaellefrm4.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=393.topic&index=9>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Why Vazaelle?</span><hr size=1> Alphonse (Ruroshen at the time) said to pick it.  I had no idea what a blue or green server was at all.<br><br>I'm glad I started on Vazaelle fairly early (Jan.23/01) so I could play EQ as intended without the serious twinkage that occurs on other servers. <p><a href=http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=40529>Abinsuran Autishzaar</A><br>Sorceror<br>Walkers of Vazaelle</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub78.ezboard.com/ucanielfaithealer.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Caniel Faithealer</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Hero</span><br> <font color=#00F500>(1/15/02 8:53:47 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub78.ezboard.com/fwalkersofvazaellefrm4.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=393.topic&index=10>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Why Vazaelle?</span><hr size=1> I heard my cousin and the son of a friend talking about eq last Christmas and decided to check it out. I bought a copy directly from Everquest and after waiting a few weeks for it to arrive, I went out and bought it at the local CompUSA. I installed it and hated it =p<br><br>A couple of weeks later the copy I bought from EQ arrived at work. Wemdar saw the box in my office and I ended up giving it to him. After hearing him talk about the game everyday for a couple of weeks, during lunch, I decided to give it another shot.<br><br>Since Wem was on Vaz I chose to play here also. Wem was an UBER level 8 ranger in Surefall - so I decided to start in Qeynos so we could play together =p<br><br>Glad I gave it another shot =) <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub78.ezboard.com/ukaosmostunebane.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Kaosmos Tunebane</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Veteran</span><br> <font color=#00F500>(1/15/02 9:19:19 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub78.ezboard.com/fwalkersofvazaellefrm4.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=393.topic&index=11>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Why Vazaelle?</span><hr size=1> I'm with you, Fieni.  I played a character once on another (green) server, then couldn't find it again and started over on Vazaelle.  I am very glad to have started on a new server--I don't think I would have liked the game at all with a mature economy and a bunch of know-it-all ubers running around. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub78.ezboard.com/urudeed.showPublicProfile?language=EN>RudeeD</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Hero</span><br> <font color=#00F500>(1/15/02 10:51:53 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub78.ezboard.com/fwalkersofvazaellefrm4.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=393.topic&index=12>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Why Vazaelle?</span><hr size=1> It was the first green one at the top of the list....I went there after my PVP experiences. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=