till on the top of the list on the chat server, its called Beautiful  hehe.  The guild creation procedure got on my nerves so I left it there, and the GM's tell me there is absolutely nothing they can do, my approved guild will remain there forever on the top of the list. <br><br>Shortly after, my other friend from Tunare came over and made a female monk named Swallows.  At level 15, in kerra ridge, a GM pops up and Swallows is reborn as Laminar.  <br><br>By this time I was certain that this server by far the best of them all, and despite character transfers and an evolving economy, it still is the best.<br> <p>Bammbi, the Ranger with the nice ass.</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub78.ezboard.com/uleopapanthera.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Leopa Panthera</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Knight</span><br> <font color=#00F500>(1/15/02 2:54:36 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub78.ezboard.com/fwalkersofvazaellefrm4.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=393.topic&index=18>Reply</a>    <br>Community Supporter<br> </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Why Vazaelle?</span><hr size=1> I deleted Nubia two weeks ago. <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :| --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/indifferent.gif ALT=":|"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br><br>She was so close to being my main instead of Leopa. I remember when we all met up in the Karanas back in our teens and made the run to Kunark (heh, I remember you jumping back on the rafts because it looked like we never got on the boat - felt sooo bad for you cause you had to wait another half hour to come back!) to meet up with Shevik and join the Walkers guild (we would also meet Dalien, Kalenie, Ulrich, and Rudee that very same weekend).<br><br>Shevik met me first on Leopa so he was surprised to see me on Nubia after he hadn't seen me for a month. He said that we needed more druids in our guild (think it was just me and Shazarae at the time) and to bring her along. So I thought, OK, I'll bring Leopa to Kunark to &quot;guild&quot; her. Once I made it to Kunark, I was immediately invited to a group with Dalien, Shevik, Whiz and whoever else and we played for hours. Met up again the next day and since they knew me as Leopa I stayed on her and then the inevitable happened ... I shot ahead of Nubia. It was a hard choice for me to make because I knew that if I got on Nubia, I would then be too low to group up with them and would forever be working to catch up since I'd be playing alone. (And making the spider run w/o sow &amp; invis is no thx.)<br><br>If I had been on Nubia when I was immediately invited to the group, it would have been a whole other story today! <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub78.ezboard.com/uhauen.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Hauen</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Squire</span><br> <font color=#00F500>(1/15/02 4:31:56 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub78.ezboard.com/fwalkersofvazaellefrm4.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=393.topic&index=19>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Why Vazaelle?</span><hr size=1> Kaosmos got the game and was having a blast, so I decided to give it a shot (swords and sorcery really aren't my bag, I'm more of a Star Trek kind of guy).  I created my first character, Sleahstack (an Iksar Shadow Knight) at midnight or so, and picked the least busy server, which happened to be...Bertoluxus or something, I can't recall now.  Kaosmos saw this and prompted me to move to Vazaelle.  He had an Iksar warrior at the time, and we spent a lot of time touring Kunark on CRs (I was always going places I wasn't supposed to be...). I got to 12 or something, he got to 16 and we both weren't very happy with our characters, so he created Kaosmos, and stuck with it.  I created Schaum (Half-Elf ranger), then Baum, then Hauen.  The rest is history. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub78.ezboard.com/umurdark.showPublicProfile?language=EN>murdark</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Squire</span><br> <font color=#00F500>(1/16/02 3:05:33 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub78.ezboard.com/fwalkersofvazaellefrm4.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=393.topic&index=20>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Why Vazaelle?</span><hr size=1> Rudee got me here i was playing on terrw mar i think that how you spell it and I Started over just to see what the server was like. Well My still here and Very Happy. <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table><table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top">  Page  <b>1</b> <a href=http://pub78.ezboard.com/fwalkersofvazaellefrm4.showMessageRange?topicID=393.topic&start=21&stop=32>2</a> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub78.ezboard.com/fwalkersofvazaellefrm4.showPrevMessage?topicID=393.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub78.ezboard.com/fwalkersofvazaellefrm4.showNextMessage?topicID=393.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a href=http://pub78.ezboard.com/fwalkersofvazaellefrm4.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=393.topic&index=20><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/professional/addReply.gif border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"><a href=http://pub78.ezboard.com/fwalkersofvazaellefrm4.threadControl?topicID=393.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/professional/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands (Moderator only)</a><br> <a href=http://p